'''Junction City''' was the capital city of [[Feriae Junction/Legends|Feriae Junction]].

Run down, but still busy with trade, Junction City contained reminders of a better time. The vast [[Grand Terminal]] was one such reminder.

After the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|destruction]] of the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|Death Star]], Junction City was crawling with spies from the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]], the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]], the [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]] and the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutts]].<ref name="TCSWE">''[[The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

